t this new MLP approximation method does indeed overcome the\ncurse of dimensionality in the numerical approximation of semilinear\nsecond-order PDEs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Sep 2020 07:37:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2020 07:55:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2020 09:31:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2020 07:05:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-12"}
